\phi\left(x\right) & =4\pi\int\dd^{3}x'G\left(x,x'\right)\rho\left(x'\right)
\end{align}

\end_inset

Probe:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\upDelta_{x}\phi\left(x\right) & =4\pi\int\dd^{3}x'\delta\left(x-x'\right)\rho\left(x'\right)=4\pi\rho\left(x\right)
\end{align*}

